{"tid":2280349,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"港情講趣●五座相連但層數不同  公屋結界玩殘外賣仔","createTime":"2020-11-10T12:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T02:37:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"570b1558b0cbd626b99ee78a0d8d5926275f95af","tid":2280349,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20201110/MZW2YBWFDBE2HF6R4R4FHJXWN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20201110%2FMZW2YBWFDBE2HF6R4R4FHJXWN4%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IrVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=cf106733\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20201110%2FMZW2YBWFDBE2HF6R4R4FHJXWN4%2F&h=19abf05c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20201110/MZW2YBWFDBE2HF6R4R4FHJXWN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港情講趣●五座相連但層數不同 <br />\n公屋結界玩殘外賣仔<br />\n<br />\n早前在社交平台有外賣員出帖，指自己去了一個「神奇屋邨」，明明進入了A座，但走了一陣子，發現自己去了B座，再走多幾走，又驚覺自己身處C座，找來找去都找不到送餐的單位，還有很多人留言說試過一樣經歷，難道&hellip;&hellip;他們都去了結界？<br />\n<br />\n其實這條「神奇屋邨」是柴灣興華二邨，在七十年代落成，是由前徙置事務處策劃興建的第七型徙置大廈，全香港只剩下這條屋邨是這種設計。全邨共有七座，因為依山而建，特色就是其中五座（展興樓、寧興樓、和興樓、豐興樓及安興樓）相連，只要入了其中一座，就可以互通去其餘四座的不同層數，剩餘兩座（樂興樓和裕興樓）亦是互通。由於每座位處的地勢水平不同，所以當你站在平台，其實也正等於身處不同座數的不同樓層，即安興樓及展興樓的八樓、寧興樓及和興樓的四樓、以及豐興樓的十六樓。如果第一次到訪，或會覺得頭暈，記者訪問前特地去走一趟，也迷了好幾次路才稍微弄清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aCrDpOKKtvsrtt77MHRRS7GHlLY=/6447x4298/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUHAAICDHNDV5BWGRL2DVDNBKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaCrDpOKKtvsrtt77MHRRS7GHlLY%3D%2F6447x4298%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUHAAICDHNDV5BWGRL2DVDNBKM.jpg&h=ac98607b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建於七十年代的柴灣興華二邨，全邨共有七座，特色就是其中五座相連。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nHZoU6vvxTBrqiMXMMjepTWfKLc=/1200x1600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PDRBD67HANGRJFWCU4EJPQYOV4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnHZoU6vvxTBrqiMXMMjepTWfKLc%3D%2F1200x1600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPDRBD67HANGRJFWCU4EJPQYOV4.jpeg&h=40658c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊式公屋的升降機不是層層停，大部份是每三層停一次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b0_3CtYa8ZZsh3q8DkgkReQi2y4=/1279x719/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VEECYCUCHVG3JHCVISGIJHLT2U.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb0_3CtYa8ZZsh3q8DkgkReQi2y4%3D%2F1279x719%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVEECYCUCHVG3JHCVISGIJHLT2U.PNG&h=0627d016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n興華二邨每座的地勢水平不同，所以當你站在平台，其實也正等於身處不同座數的不同樓層。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SbvAih1CDnNvVy3fFDh0tcez5WU=/1276x785/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MV6LSVA2FAJLIMAALFUMQSESE.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSbvAih1CDnNvVy3fFDh0tcez5WU%3D%2F1276x785%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MV6LSVA2FAJLIMAALFUMQSESE.PNG&h=dc44e3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n興華二邨居民主要靠兩部大升降機，由環翠道地面到達豐興樓21樓的天台，或到16樓的平台再通往不同座數。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NoXhRG6QBIW87O7N89BPJWKSs3M=/1600x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PDT6V6JCBNBRPNQALHNLZKGTTY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNoXhRG6QBIW87O7N89BPJWKSs3M%3D%2F1600x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPDT6V6JCBNBRPNQALHNLZKGTTY.jpeg&h=9ac790a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要入了其中一座，就可以互通去其餘四座的不同層數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n靠聽聲尋戶主 貼士鬆手<br />\n<br />\n曾多次送餐到興華二邨的外賣員David，幾乎每次都被考起，因為一層動輒七八十個單位，好比一個迷宮，「樓梯都係麻煩，落錯會去了倔頭路，又要上樓梯走回頭路才能離開，幾座都是這樣，我試過兜了十五分鐘，再打給客人，他在門口大嗌，我沿着聲音尋找才到達他的單位。」他幾乎每次送餐都要出動GPS，送一次外賣的時間，已足以到其他屋邨送兩次，David直言勝在邨民夠「鬆手」，會給予貼士才會繼續樂於接單。<br />\n<br />\n興華二邨居民主要靠乘搭兩部大升降機，由環翠道地面到達位於豐興樓十六樓的平台，再穿過空中走廊去到相應的樓宇，但這部升降機還能去到二十一樓的天台，而天台又同樣能接駁到五座的出入口，所以送外賣前，又要計一計數。「因為天台（豐興樓二十一樓）和平台（豐興樓的十六樓）相差五層，如果要去十八樓，在兩層出𨋢都可以，但如果去十七樓，在十六樓出𨋢會快過上天台再走下來。」聽完David一輪講解，其實在這邨遊走，除了要識計數，更重要的是要頭腦清醒。<br />\n<br />\n到底這屋邨的建築師為何要將幾座樓連在一起？我們邀請了房屋署前建築師衞翠芷博士到興華二邨走一趟。未曾踏足該屋。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這幾座舊式公屋還有另一特色，升降機每隔三層才停，所以大部份居民出入都要上落樓梯，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了房署，房協亦有興建公共屋邨，例如勵德邨、乙明邨等，全部設計都較房署出品時尚得多，衞博士說：。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了上述的興華二邨，香港還有很多不同類型的公屋設計，衞博士最喜歡的，就是華富邨。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"2e76851e313c96f955147ee8dbaa0084cc31d324","tid":2280349,"uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"華富邨依山臨海 經典之作<br />\n<br />\n華富邨風景可媲美千萬豪宅，臨海的幾座採用長條形設計，屋外一條長走廊，無遮無掩，夠晒通風，以前的走廊常用來晾衫、打麻雀、踩單車，可謂屋邨特色，亦是大眾集體回憶。然而，時代變遷自有取捨，此情此景不復在，衞博士說：「現在是整潔得多，但沒有以前那種生氣。」如此一來，相比現今的新公屋設計千篇一律，衞博士又會否覺得新不如舊？「我覺得每個時代的設計都是融合了當時需要，公屋始終不能像私樓般，搞很多花款吸客，一定是最基本，適合住戶使用為前提，不同年代有不同設計，總不能批評哪個年代較好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KKrdAp_iRAoymNwb9C2gbWeaJFE=/1600x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JJA4BTKKYRHMXAUUS45NWWEAZQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKKrdAp_iRAoymNwb9C2gbWeaJFE%3D%2F1600x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJJA4BTKKYRHMXAUUS45NWWEAZQ.jpeg&h=75c0157e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵盛西邨的空中走廊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NYWNe5iuqGlYi0Cl4gKCcZQ6gDA=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N5XIRB5LLRGQ7GOWZTTDH4CPS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNYWNe5iuqGlYi0Cl4gKCcZQ6gDA%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN5XIRB5LLRGQ7GOWZTTDH4CPS4.jpg&h=5b7bd352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾多次送餐到興華二邨的外賣員David，幾乎每次都要出動GPS尋找目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XiamDmrASVntjvTe5NbwQLnXRpQ=/1606x902/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OXRKDZW6OBE5JDK2HGTRXQWML4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXiamDmrASVntjvTe5NbwQLnXRpQ%3D%2F1606x902%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOXRKDZW6OBE5JDK2HGTRXQWML4.png&h=aa93f7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港眾多公共屋邨，房屋署前建築師衞翠芷博士最喜歡華富邨的設計。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港其他特色公屋設計<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YsgqOkjJUHOp4VhMw48DKaxMtn4=/437x292/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MKS4RSNBZJH6DKTO3JEOSAL5NU.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYsgqOkjJUHOp4VhMw48DKaxMtn4%3D%2F437x292%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMKS4RSNBZJH6DKTO3JEOSAL5NU.PNG&h=65d0a6c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蝴蝶邨，梯級型設計，屋邨所有單位的設計一樣，以一至四人的家庭為主，是全港獨有設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WBkS2UJFUVAOzrH65_vj32VOxFY=/6593x4395/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NITCFTEK6RG5DJBC3T267TQN2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWBkS2UJFUVAOzrH65_vj32VOxFY%3D%2F6593x4395%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNITCFTEK6RG5DJBC3T267TQN2M.jpg&h=d58c9c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長安邨，Y3型設計，每層電梯大堂面積不一，每三層由上至下呈梯級型設計。佔地較大，較常見於新市鎮，如青衣、將軍澳等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IDalyJqzLJITMyQgQV8ocIxyHg8=/4700x3525/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QTD42WSNTBEBJBHQOVUYH25EPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIDalyJqzLJITMyQgQV8ocIxyHg8%3D%2F4700x3525%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQTD42WSNTBEBJBHQOVUYH25EPE.jpg&h=004176db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華富邨，雙塔式大廈（井字形），香港首幢井字型公屋的所在地，大廈中央設有一個巨大天井，在1984年後已停止興建。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GYn3zNyQrSRSbknygncZWHpais4=/2235x1534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K3QGEH4G7FDWBIMUEQWXRJ46CI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGYn3zNyQrSRSbknygncZWHpais4%3D%2F2235x1534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK3QGEH4G7FDWBIMUEQWXRJ46CI.jpg&h=c77f90dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勵德邨，圓筒形設計，房協興建，香港唯一採用圓筒形設計的公屋，設計有助白天採光及空氣對流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/onRzaEhTKWxhnqXVb4besFTwMNQ=/5472x3648/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6RVLUYMNCRBTJHPGRUDDLFZZCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FonRzaEhTKWxhnqXVb4besFTwMNQ%3D%2F5472x3648%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6RVLUYMNCRBTJHPGRUDDLFZZCA.jpg&h=c670c34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大興邨，斜面十字型設計，目的是讓低層住戶有較多採光面積，全港共建有八幢，分別位於屯門大興邨及觀塘順安邨。<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃子配<br />\n<br />\n攝影：張洛晞、潘志恆"},{"pid":"3cf1615e7405d3fb94e4c7d4d74ffe3ed4cdbce7","tid":2280349,"uid":14952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:54:40.000Z","msg":"S<img 